<P>
Libyan leader Moammar Kadafi has decided to cut off or trim the flow of funds 
to some liberation and terrorist groups, Western and Palestinian sources said. 
The sources, in Tripoli over the weekend for ceremonies marking the 20th 
anniversary of the coup that brought Kadafi to power, said he has told several 
